Content-Type: application/json

{"type":"payment_intent.succeeded","data":{"object":{"id":"pi_test","amount_received":12345,"metadata":{"order_id":"1"}}}}

### PIX webhook
POST https://<seu-projeto>.vercel.app/api/webhooks/pix
x-pix-signature: {{hmac}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"txid":"abc","status":"CONFIRMED","amount_cents":9900,"metadata":{"order_id":"1"}}

